{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">&quot;We, my sister and I, have long lived abroad, together with the longing for our homeland. Not long ago, we received an invitation to a party in Romania, in the Carpathians. My sister, without hesitation, got into the car and left. I refused to go, but after some time I received a terrifying message from my sister. Frightened, I dropped everything and quickly set out to find her. I wonder what happened?&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Strigoi is a first-person horror shooter set in the Carpathian Mountains. You will face various enemies (Vampires, Strigoi...), encounter interesting puzzles, and find different items that will help you overcome obstacles and enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Game Features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A semi-open world with various interesting locations such as Mountains, Dungeons, a Village, Graveyards, an Abandoned Castle, and more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dangerous and terrifying enemies for whom you are merely food and an unwelcome guest.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A deep storyline where you must unravel the mysteries of this world.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A game world filled with dangers, including not only enemies but also traps and puzzles.</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081670/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737304488","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081670/page.bg.jpg?t=1737304488","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081670/811660eb1f4f1f577db707d42a85abdf5f1e989d/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1737304488","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3081670/811660eb1f4f1f577db707d42a85abdf5f1e989d/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1737304488","categori